	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-173489384" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/04/10/1950253/more-books-than-ever-targeted-for-bans">More Books Than Ever Targeted For Bans</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://sherwood.news/culture/record-number-of-books-targeted-for-bans-in-us/"  title="External link - https://sherwood.news/culture/record-number-of-books-targeted-for-bans-in-us/" target="_blank"> (sherwood.news) </a></span></span>

		
		
